reqs:
Pre-reqs: All of NURS 302, NURS 303, NURS 304, NURS 305, NURS 306.
Co-reqs: Either (a) one of NURS 338, NURS 339, NURS 340 or (b) one of NURS 341, NURS 342, NURS 343. ((depending on sequencing of NURS 333 with other professional practice courses.))
Equivalents:
courseName: Professional Nursing Practice with Childbearing Individuals and Families
description: Analysis and application of theories, concepts, evidence and competencies guiding professional nursing practice with childbearing individuals and families during the transition to parenthood in a variety of practice settings and contexts.
